3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a hidden Markov model-based approach for bistatic delay estimation, which involves system modeling and control theory. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses the Baum-Welch algorithm for parameter estimation in the HMM-based approach, which involves machine learning and pattern recognition. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may involve software implementation and testing of the proposed approach, which involves software engineering principles and practices.
